                <h1>How Long Does a DISA Background Check Take?</h1>
                <p>The duration of a DISA background check can vary based on several factors such as the scope of the check and the specific background information required. Typically, these checks take anywhere from a few days to 2 weeks. However, complexities such as discrepancies or additional investigations can extend the timeline further.</p>
